title: I heard that there is wreckage from a plane crash in the 1960\'s still in the Green Swamp. Is this true?
text:
This story keeps getting better. Apparently a guy from Illinois
hauled the plane out by helicopter and took it home to be restored.
Here's a link to more info about that:
http://www.warbirdregistry.org/p47registry/p47-415920.html
